rong>[[Resist the voices in your head as you play Match-3 games in your dreams. Remember, if you don't get a high enough score, you may never wake up.]]</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743380/extras/0942242e0600af6c334348421819d7ba.avif?t=1635188270\" width=500 height=150 /></span><br><br>---YOUR CHOICES DETERMINE YOUR FATE---<br>THE DECISIONS YOU MAKE IN YOUR CONSCIOUS AND SUBCONSCIOUS HOURS DETERMINE THE BRANCH YOUR STORY TAKES.<br><br><strong>[[Choose dialogue options and pick how to play the Match-3 sections to change the outcome of the story.]]</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743380/extras/86a8949bb882ce311dddf837ecee71ab.avif?t=1635188270\" width=500 height=150 /></span>",
